["TEXT","e15276",1545,800,0,"17.STB4: Strobe pulse 4 選通脈衝4\n18. STB5: Strobe pulse 5 選通脈衝5\n19.STB6: Strobe pulse 6 選通脈衝6\n20.GND: Ground for printing 打印接地\n21.GND: Ground for printing 打印接地\n22.CLK: Print clock input 打印頭时鐘輸入\n23.DI: Print data input 打印頭數據輸入\n24.M_VCC: Print head drive power supply\n打印頭驅動電源\n25.M_VCC: Print head drive power supply \n打印頭驅動電源\n26.NC: No Connection 空口-冇連接\n27.NC: No Connection 空口-冇連接\n28.PHE: Sensor (Photoelectric on/off type) Emitter \n傳感器（光電通斷型) 發射極\n29.3V3: Sensor (Photoelectric on/off type) Power Supply \n傳感器（光電通斷型) 電源\n30.PHK: Sensor (Photoelectric on/off type) Cathode \n傳感器（光電通斷型) 陰極","st2",0]
["TEXT","e15369",1545,930,0,"1.M_B+: Stepper motor phase B+ 步進電機相位\n2.M_B-: Stepper motor phase B  步進電機相位\n3.M_A+: Stepper motor phase A+ 步進電機相位\n4.M_A-: Stepper motor phase A 步進電機相位\n8.LAT: Data latch control 數據鎖存控制\n9.GND: Ground for printing 打印接地\n10.GND: Ground for printing 打印接地\n11.STB1: Strobe pulse 1 選通脈衝\n12.STB2: Strobe pulse 2 選通脈衝\n13.STB3: Strobe pulse 3 選通脈衝\n14.THER: Thermistor terminal 熱敏電阻端\n15.GND: Ground for printing 打印地\n16.3V3: Logic power supply port 邏輯電源端口","st2",0]
